* They say
love will find a way *

40:48.113 --> 40:54.085
* But I'll tell you what
at the end of the day *

40:54.119 --> 40:59.658
* Maybe love
ain't even real *

40:59.691 --> 41:02.460
* But I believe

41:02.494 --> 41:06.097
* In Sheffield Steel

41:06.131 --> 41:09.668
* Sheffield steel

41:09.701 --> 41:11.837
Hello, hello. Kim Brown's
famous baked tuna surprise.
Shh-shh-shh!

41:11.870 --> 41:13.639
* More than I

41:13.672 --> 41:17.676
* Could say for you

41:17.709 --> 41:20.612
* You've touched my heart

41:20.646 --> 41:22.781
* And you made me feel

