* Your knife forged out
of Sheffield Steel *

41:28.987 --> 41:31.322
* The eyes can pierce

41:31.356 --> 41:34.660
That's a great song.
Oh, you're kidding me.

41:34.693 --> 41:37.629
What's wrong with you?
That's right up your alley.

41:37.663 --> 41:40.465
- He doesn't like the song?
- You don't like the song?

41:40.498 --> 41:43.501
Great song.
I wish I wrote it.

41:43.535 --> 41:46.004
* But I missed the knife

41:46.037 --> 41:48.707
* That you put
deep inside me *

41:48.740 --> 41:51.643
Well?
You betcha.

41:51.677 --> 41:55.313
If we sprinkled rice
on our hair,
I'd even feel married.

41:55.346 --> 41:57.883
Oh, you're scared.

41:57.916 --> 42:00.852
Oh, good.
No, we do not
have to get married.

42:00.886 --> 42:03.722
But we should get
comfortable.

42:04.756 --> 42:07.158
Come here.
I'll break the ice.

42:07.192 --> 42:09.194
** [ Continues ]

42:09.227 --> 42:11.830
Mmm.
There you go.

42:11.863 --> 42:14.332
It's just like
falling off a log.

42:14.365 --> 42:16.668
Annie, I'll--
Go get some ice.

42:16.702 --> 42:19.671
We're gonna see how many
uses we can put it to.

42:19.705 --> 42:23.341
When you get back,
I'll give you
a big surprise.

42:23.374 --> 42:25.844
Hmm.
You know what?

42:25.877 --> 42:27.846
What?
You're all right.

42:27.879 --> 42:29.715
You're all right, too.

42:33.719 --> 42:36.421
Hurry up!

42:36.454 --> 42:40.525
* They say I don't know
if a broken heart can heal *

42:40.558 --> 42:44.863
* But not a heart
made of Sheffield Steel *

42:44.896 --> 42:46.865
Tom.

42:46.898 --> 42:49.534
* Sheffield Steel
Tom.

